{%- comment -%} Dedicated mattress product page — layout: Sonno reference, Klawford branding {%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign kl_first_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant -%}
{%- assign kl_on_sale = false -%}
{%- if product.compare_at_price > product.price -%}{%- assign kl_on_sale = true -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- assign kl_sale_pct = 0 -%}
{%- if kl_on_sale -%}
  {%- assign kl_sale_pct = product.compare_at_price | minus: product.price | times: 100 | divided_by: product.compare_at_price | round -%}
{%- endif -%}

<div class="klm-page">

  {%- comment -%} ── BREADCRUMB ──────────────────────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="klm-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M3 1l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      {%- if collection -%}
        <a href="{{ collection.url }}">{{ collection.title }}</a>
        <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M3 1l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      {%- endif -%}
      <span>{{ product.title }}</span>
    </nav>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} ── PRODUCT TOP: GALLERY + INFO ──────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="klm-top container">

    {%- comment -%} ── GALLERY ─────────────────────────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="klm-gallery">
      <div class="klm-gallery__main" id="klm-gallery-main">
        {%- if product.featured_image -%}
          <img
            id="klm-main-img"
            class="klm-gallery__main-img"
            src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 900 }}"
            srcset="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w,
                    {{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 900 }} 900w,
                    {{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 1200 }} 1200w"
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw"
            alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape | default: product.title }}"
            width="900" height="675"
            loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="klm-gallery__placeholder">
            <svg width="80" height="60" viewBox="0 0 80 60" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="4" y="8" width="72" height="44" rx="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
              <rect x="10" y="16" width="60" height="28" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/>
              <circle cx="28" cy="26" r="5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <path d="M16 40l18-14 14 10 10-8 10 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <p>Upload product images in Shopify Admin</p>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
        <span class="klm-gallery__badge">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><path d="M7 4v3l2 2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          60 Night Risk-Free Trial
        </span>
        <button class="klm-gallery__expand" id="klm-expand" type="button" aria-label="Expand image">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M1 6V1h5M10 1h5v5M15 10v5h-5M6 15H1v-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          Click To Expand
        </button>
      </div>

      {%- if product.images.size > 1 -%}
        <div class="klm-gallery__thumb-wrap">
          <button class="klm-gallery__arrow" id="klm-thumb-prev" type="button" aria-label="Previous images">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M9 2L4 7l5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="klm-gallery__thumbs" id="klm-thumbs">
            {%- for image in product.images -%}
              <button
                class="klm-gallery__thumb{% if forloop.first %} is-active{% endif %}"
                type="button"
                data-src="{{ image | image_url: width: 900 }}"
                aria-label="View image {{ forloop.index }}">
                <img src="{{ image | image_url: width: 160 }}" alt="{{ image.alt | escape | default: product.title }}" width="80" height="80" loading="lazy">
              </button>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
          <button class="klm-gallery__arrow" id="klm-thumb-next" type="button" aria-label="Next images">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M5 2l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      {%- else -%}
        <div class="klm-gallery__thumb-wrap">
          {%- for i in (1..5) -%}
            <div class="klm-gallery__thumb-ph">
              <svg width="24" height="18" viewBox="0 0 80 60" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="4" y="8" width="72" height="44" rx="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"/><circle cx="28" cy="26" r="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M16 46l18-18 14 12 10-10 10 16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
            </div>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} ── PRODUCT INFO ──────────────────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="klm-info">

      <div class="klm-info__rating">
        <div class="klm-stars" aria-label="4.8 out of 5">
          {%- for i in (1..5) -%}
            <svg class="klm-star" viewBox="0 0 14 13" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7 .5l1.76 3.56L13 4.75l-3 2.92.71 4.12L7 9.77l-3.71 2.02.71-4.12L1 4.75l4.24-.69L7 .5z"/></svg>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
        <a href="#klm-faq" class="klm-info__review-link">
          4.8/5 &mdash; {{ section.settings.review_count | default: '4,210' }} Reviews
        </a>
      </div>

      <h1 class="klm-info__title">{{ product.title }}</h1>

      <div class="klm-info__price-row" id="klm-price-row">
        <span class="klm-info__price" id="klm-price">{{ kl_first_variant.price | money }}</span>
        {%- if kl_on_sale -%}
          <span class="klm-info__compare" id="klm-compare">{{ kl_first_variant.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
          <span class="klm-info__pct" id="klm-pct">{{ kl_sale_pct }}% OFF</span>
        {%- else -%}
          <span class="klm-info__compare" id="klm-compare" style="display:none;"></span>
          <span class="klm-info__pct" id="klm-pct" style="display:none;"></span>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      {%- comment -%} Size selector {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- form 'product', product, id: 'klm-form' -%}
        {%- unless product.has_only_default_variant -%}
          {%- for option in product.options_with_values -%}
            {%- assign _olc = option.name | downcase -%}
            {%- if _olc == 'size' -%}
              {%- assign _selected_price = kl_first_variant.price -%}
              <div class="klm-size-wrap">
                <div class="klm-size-box">
                  <div class="klm-size-header">
                    <span class="klm-size-header__label">Select Size</span>
                    <span class="klm-size-header__current" id="klm-size-name">{{ option.selected_value }}</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="klm-size-grid">
                    {%- for value in option.values -%}
                      {%- assign _sv_price = 0 -%}
                      {%- assign _sv_compare = 0 -%}
                      {%- assign _sv_id = '' -%}
                      {%- assign _sv_avail = false -%}
                      {%- for v in product.variants -%}
                        {%- if v.option1 == value or v.option2 == value or v.option3 == value -%}
                          {%- assign _sv_price = v.price -%}
                          {%- assign _sv_compare = v.compare_at_price -%}
                          {%- assign _sv_id = v.id -%}
                          {%- assign _sv_avail = v.available -%}
                          {%- break -%}
                        {%- endif -%}
                      {%- endfor -%}
                      {%- assign _price_diff = _sv_price | minus: _selected_price -%}
                      <button type="button"
                        class="klm-size-btn{% if option.selected_value == value %} is-active{% endif %}{% unless _sv_avail %} is-soldout{% endunless %}"
                        data-size="{{ value | escape }}"
                        data-vid="{{ _sv_id }}"
                        data-price="{{ _sv_price }}"
                        data-compare="{{ _sv_compare }}"
                        aria-pressed="{% if option.selected_value == value %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}">
                        <div class="klm-size-btn__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                          <svg viewBox="0 0 56 34" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <rect x="1" y="1" width="54" height="5" rx="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/>
                            <rect x="1" y="6" width="54" height="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
                            <path d="M14 6v8M28 6v8M42 6v8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.7"/>
                            <rect x="1" y="14" width="54" height="13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
                            <path d="M9 14v13M19 14v13M28 14v13M37 14v13M47 14v13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-dasharray="1.5 1.5"/>
                            <rect x="1" y="27" width="54" height="6" rx="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
                          </svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="klm-size-btn__name">{{ value }}</span>
                        {%- if option.selected_value == value -%}
                          <span class="klm-size-btn__price" data-role="price">{{ _sv_price | money }}</span>
                        {%- elsif _price_diff < 0 -%}
                          {%- assign _diff_abs = _price_diff | abs -%}
                          <span class="klm-size-btn__price klm-size-btn__price--save" data-role="price">-{{ _diff_abs | money }}</span>
                        {%- elsif _price_diff > 0 -%}
                          <span class="klm-size-btn__price" data-role="price">+{{ _price_diff | money }}</span>
                        {%- else -%}
                          <span class="klm-size-btn__price" data-role="price">{{ _sv_price | money }}</span>
                        {%- endif -%}
                      </button>
                    {%- endfor -%}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
        {%- endunless -%}

        <input type="hidden" name="id" id="klm-variant-id" value="{{ kl_first_variant.id }}">

        <button
          type="submit"
          class="btn btn--primary btn--full klm-atc"
          id="klm-atc-btn"
          data-add-to-cart
          {%- unless kl_first_variant.available -%}disabled{%- endunless -%}>
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M1 1h2.5l1.7 8.6a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.4h7.3a2 2 0 0 0 2-1.6L17.5 4H4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="7" cy="15.5" r="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/><circle cx="13.5" cy="15.5" r="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/></svg>
          <span id="klm-atc-label">{%- if kl_first_variant.available -%}Add to Basket{%- else -%}Sold Out{%- endif -%}</span>
        </button>
      {%- endform -%}

      <div class="klm-payment-info">
        <div class="klm-payment-info__row">
          <svg width="16" height="12" viewBox="0 0 18 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M1 2h11v9H1V2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><path d="M12 5h3l2 3v3h-5V5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><circle cx="4" cy="12" r="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><circle cx="14" cy="12" r="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/></svg>
          <span><strong>Fast Free delivery.</strong> Select date at checkout.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="klm-payment-info__row">
          <span class="klm-logo klm-logo--dividebuy">Divide<em>Buy</em></span>
          <span>{{ section.settings.dividebuy_text | default: 'Spread the cost interest-free over 12 months, 0% credit.' }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="klm-payment-info__row" style="border-bottom:none;">
          <span class="klm-logo klm-logo--klarna">Klarna.</span>
          <span>{{ section.settings.klarna_text | default: 'Pay later in 30 days or split into 3 interest-free payments.' }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="klm-payment-info__icons">
          {%- render 'payment-icons', extended: true -%}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{%- comment -%} ── TRUST STRIP ─────────────────────────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="klm-trust-strip">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="klm-trust-strip__inner">
      <div class="klm-trust-item">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13 3l2.5 5 5.5.8-4 3.9 1 5.5-5-2.6L8 17.2l1-5.5L5 7.8l5.5-.8L13 3z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        <div><strong>5 Year Warranty</strong><span>On every mattress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="klm-trust-item">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="13" cy="13" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M13 8v5l3 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        <div><strong>60 Night Risk-Free Trial</strong><span>Sleep on it first</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="klm-trust-item">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="6" width="20" height="4" rx="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M5 10h16v10a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V10z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M10 10v12M16 10v12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/></svg>
        <div><strong>0% Interest Rate</strong><span>Spread the cost</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="klm-trust-item">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 18h20M3 18l3-8h14l3 8M9 18v-3m8 3v-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="7" cy="20" r="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><circle cx="19" cy="20" r="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/></svg>
        <div><strong>Fast Free Delivery</strong><span>Room of your choice</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="klm-trust-item">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="4" y="6" width="18" height="3" rx="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/><rect x="3" y="9" width="20" height="12" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M9 15h8M9 18h5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        <div><strong>UK Quality Materials</strong><span>Built to last</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{%- comment -%} ── RATING BANNER ────────────────────────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="klm-rating-banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="klm-rating-banner__inner">
      <h2 class="klm-rating-banner__heading">Over {{ section.settings.customer_count | default: '10,000' }} Happy Customers</h2>
      <div class="klm-rating-banner__stars">
        {%- for i in (1..5) -%}
          <svg class="klm-star klm-star--lg" viewBox="0 0 14 13" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7 .5l1.76 3.56L13 4.75l-3 2.92.71 4.12L7 9.77l-3.71 2.02.71-4.12L1 4.75l4.24-.69L7 .5z"/></svg>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
      <p class="klm-rating-banner__sub">Rated 4.8/5 based on {{ section.settings.review_count | default: '4,210' }} verified reviews</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{%- comment -%} ── WHAT MAKES OUR MATTRESS GREAT ───────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
<section class="klm-features" id="klm-features">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="klm-section__heading">What Makes Our Mattress Great</h2>
    <div class="klm-features__body">

      {%- comment -%} Left: product image {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="klm-features__image">
        {%- if product.featured_image -%}
          <img
            src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 700 }}"
            alt="{{ product.title }}"
            width="700" height="560"
            loading="lazy"
            class="klm-features__image-img">
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="klm-features__image-ph">
            <svg width="64" height="48" viewBox="0 0 80 60" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="4" y="8" width="72" height="44" rx="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"/><circle cx="28" cy="28" r="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M16 44l16-16 14 12 10-10 10 14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span>Upload a product image to display here</span>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      {%- comment -%} Right: icon tabs + indicator + detail {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="klm-features__right">
        <div class="klm-features__icon-row" id="klm-feat-icons" role="tablist">
          {%- assign _feat_names = 'Air Vents,Hypoallergenic,Orthopaedic,Washable Cover,Pressure Relief,Temp Regulation,Motion Isolation,UK Quality' | split: ',' -%}
          {%- for f in _feat_names -%}
            <button class="klm-feat{% if forloop.first %} is-active{% endif %}" role="tab" data-feat="{{ forloop.index0 }}" type="button" aria-selected="{% if forloop.first %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}">
              <div class="klm-feat__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                {%- case forloop.index0 -%}
                  {%- when 0 -%}<!-- Air Vents -->
                    <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round">
                      <path d="M3 9q3.5 4 7 0t7 0t7 0"/>
                      <path d="M3 15q3.5 4 7 0t7 0t7 0"/>
                      <path d="M3 21q3.5 4 7 0t7 0t7 0"/>
                    </svg>
                  {%- when 1 -%}<!-- Hypoallergenic -->
                    <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M15 4L6 8v7c0 5.5 4 9 9 11 5-2 9-5.5 9-11V8L15 4z"/>
                      <path d="M11 15l3 3 5.5-5.5"/>
                    </svg>
                  {%- when 2 -%}<!-- Orthopaedic -->
                    <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <circle cx="15" cy="6" r="3"/>
                      <path d="M15 9c-3 2-4 5-3 8l1 5"/>
                      <path d="M15 9c3 2 4 5 3 8l-1 5"/>
                      <path d="M10 22h10"/>
                      <path d="M12 17h6"/>
                    </svg>
                  {%- when 3 -%}<!-- Washable Cover -->
                    <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round">
                      <rect x="4" y="9" width="22" height="17" rx="3" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                      <circle cx="15" cy="18" r="5"/>
                      <path d="M7 13V9"/>
                      <circle cx="7" cy="13" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
                      <path d="M10 4h4M17 4h3"/>
                    </svg>
                  {%- when 4 -%}<!-- Pressure Relief -->
                    <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <circle cx="15" cy="7" r="3"/>
                      <path d="M10 27V17a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v10"/>
                      <path d="M6 27h18"/>
                      <path d="M10 21c-2-1-4-1-4 1"/>
                      <path d="M20 21c2-1 4-1 4 1"/>
                    </svg>
                  {%- when 5 -%}<!-- Temp Regulation -->
                    <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round">
                      <path d="M15 5v14.2"/>
                      <path d="M11 5h8"/>
                      <path d="M11 9h4"/>
                      <path d="M11 13h4"/>
                      <circle cx="15" cy="23" r="3"/>
                      <path d="M18 19.2V23"/>
                    </svg>
                  {%- when 6 -%}<!-- Motion Isolation -->
                    <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <rect x="2" y="16" width="26" height="10" rx="2"/>
                      <path d="M15 16V10"/>
                      <circle cx="8" cy="9" r="3"/>
                      <path d="M5 16v-1a3 3 0 0 1 6 0v1"/>
                      <circle cx="22" cy="9" r="3"/>
                      <path d="M19 16v-1a3 3 0 0 1 6 0v1"/>
                    </svg>
                  {%- when 7 -%}<!-- UK Quality -->
                    <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <path d="M8 10l2-5 5 3 5-3 2 5"/>
                      <path d="M6 10h18v8a9 9 0 0 1-18 0v-8z"/>
                      <path d="M11 19l4-4 4 4"/>
                      <path d="M15 15v6"/>
                    </svg>
                {%- endcase -%}
              </div>
              <span class="klm-feat__label">{{ f }}</span>
            </button>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>

        <div class="klm-features__track" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="klm-features__pip" id="klm-feat-pip"></span>
        </div>

        <div class="klm-features__detail">
          <h3 class="klm-features__detail-title" id="klm-feat-title">Air Vents</h3>
          <p class="klm-features__detail-body" id="klm-feat-body">Built-in ventilation channels draw heat and moisture away from the mattress core, keeping the sleeping surface fresh and breathable throughout the night.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{%- comment -%} ── OVERVIEW ────────────────────────────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
<section class="klm-section klm-overview">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="klm-section__heading">Overview</h2>
    <div class="klm-overview__body rte">
      {{ product.description }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{%- comment -%} ── SLEEP TECHNOLOGY ─────────────────────────────────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
<section class="klm-sleep-tech">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="klm-sleep-tech__inner">
      <div class="klm-sleep-tech__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="56" height="56" viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none"><path d="M28 8a20 20 0 0 0 20 20A20 20 0 0 1 28 48 20 20 0 0 1 8 28 20 20 0 0 0 28 8z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="38" cy="16" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><circle cx="44" cy="22" r="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="klm-sleep-tech__heading">Get Ready for Your Best Night's Sleep</h2>
      <p class="klm-sleep-tech__body">Every Klawford mattress is engineered around one goal — helping you sleep longer, deeper, and more comfortably, every single night.</p>
      <h3 class="klm-sleep-tech__sub">What Our Comfort System Delivers</h3>
      <ul class="klm-sleep-tech__list">
        <li>
          <div class="klm-sleep-tech__bullet-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><rect x="2" y="7" width="16" height="6" rx="1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><path d="M4 7V5m3 2V4m3 3V5m3 2V4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M4 13v2m3-2v1m3-1v2m3-2v1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Comfort layers are calibrated to cushion pressure points at your hips, shoulders, and lower back — so you wake up without stiffness, whatever position you sleep in.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="klm-sleep-tech__bullet-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 0 0 8 8A8 8 0 0 1 10 18 8 8 0 0 1 2 10 8 8 0 0 0 10 2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Temperature-regulating materials work through the night to keep you at the ideal sleep temperature — not too warm, not too cool, all night long.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="klm-sleep-tech__bullet-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M4 10h12M4 6l4 4-4 4M12 6l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Motion isolation ensures that movement on one side of the mattress stays there — you sleep undisturbed, even if your partner shifts or gets up during the night.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

